-widget"><div id="text-2" class="widget-wrapper widget_text"><div id="widget-title-one" class="widget-title-home"><h3 class="widget-title-home">What is a Value Rating?</h3></div><div class="textwidget"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2016/05/value-rating-sign-post.jpg" width="300px" align="center" /><br><br>Your <a href="https://calculatedriskinc.com/value-rating/">Value Rating</a> is a single number that lets you rank complex choices from most to least desirable. The key to your Value Rating is unveiling your Preference Profile: a personalized and quantified signature of what matters to you -- and how strongly.</div></div></div><!-- home-widget-1 --><div id="home_widget_2" class="home-widget"><div id="text-3" class="widget-wrapper widget_text"><div id="widget-title-two" class="widget-title-home"><h3 class="widget-title-home">One size does not fit all</h3></div><div class="textwidget"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2016/05/one-size-does-not-fit-all.jpg" width="300px" /><br><br>We have all seen Top 10 lists and Blue Ribbon designations claiming to identify the best performers. With a momentâ€™s reflection, of course, we understand that one size cannot fit all. Choosing among complex options demands a <a href="https://calculatedriskinc.com/tailored-solutions/">tailored approach</a> that suits you.</div></div></div><!-- home-widget-2 --><div id="home_widget_3" class="home-widget"><div id="text-5" class="widget-wrapper widget_text"><div id="widget-title-three" class="widget-title-home"><h3 class="widget-title-home">What&#8217;s your Preference Profile?</h3></div><div class="textwidget"><img src="wp-content/uploads/2016/05/preference-profile.jpg" width="300px" /><br><br>When choices are complex, revealing your Preference Profile is the key to creating meaningful and personalized Value Ratings. Our approach guides you through the <a href="https://calculatedriskinc.com/methodology/">discovery process</a> to reveal your personal Preference Profile.</div></div></div><!-- home-wid